> Error invoking function 'hubdb_table_rows'
Hello is anyone having any issues with HubDB in custom modules on staging pages? HubDB just isnt working for me on my staging page.
Can u assign contact.property_name to a variable first and then do `{% for row in hubdb_table_rows(1234, "dbcolumn_name=~variable_name") %}`

```{% set string_var = "{{ contact.property_name }}" %}```
Then using {{ string_var }}, might have confused myself here, assuming the expression would bring up the same error?
